participant_id.Description: Unique BIDS identifier for the participant in this study.

iqc_t2_1_pc_score.Description: T2 #1: Protocol compliance score of 1 (pass) or 0 (fail)

iqc_t2_1_complete.Description: T2 #1: DAIC received correct number of files for this series (1=pass, 0=fail)

iqc_t2_1_brain_mean.Description: T2 #1: Mean intensity within brain mask

iqc_t2_1_brain_std.Description: T2 #1: Standard deviation of intensities within brain mask

iqc_t2_2_pc_score.Description: T2 #2: Protocol compliance score of 1 (pass) or 0 (fail)

iqc_t2_2_complete.Description: T2 #2: DAIC received correct number of files for this series (1=pass, 0=fail)

iqc_t2_2_brain_mean.Description: T2 #2: Mean intensity within brain mask

iqc_t2_2_brain_std.Description: T2 #2: Standard deviation of intensities within brain mask

iqc_t2_3_pc_score.Description: T2 #3: Protocol compliance score of 1 (pass) or 0 (fail)

iqc_t2_3_complete.Description: T2 #3: DAIC received correct number of files for this series (1=pass, 0=fail)

iqc_t2_3_brain_mean.Description: T2 #3: Mean intensity within brain mask

iqc_t2_3_brain_std.Description: T2 #3: Standard deviation of intensities within brain mask

iqc_t2_total_passpc.Description: T2: Number that passed protocol compliance

iqc_t2_total_passqc.Description: T2: Number that passed visual quality control (QC)

iqc_t2_good_ser.Description: T2: Number that passed protocol compliance and QC

iqc_t2_ok_ser.Description: T2: Number of series that are complete and passed QC (ignoring PC)

iqc_t2_bad_ser.Description: T2: Number that failed either protocol compliance or QC

iqc_t2_ser_pc_issues.Description: T2: Number with protocol compliance issues

iqc_t2_ser_incomp.Description: T2: Number of series missing files at DAIC

iqc_t2_other_qc.Description: T2: Number with other QC issue

iqc_t2_all_voxvol.Description: T2: Mean volume of single for all scans (mm^3)

iqc_t2_ok_voxvol.Description: T2: Mean volume of single voxel averaged across all OK scans (mm^3)

iqc_t2_all_brainvol.Description: T2: Mean volume of brain mask averaged across all scans (mm^3)

iqc_t2_ok_brainvol.Description: T2: Mean volume of brain mask averaged across all OK scans (mm^3)

iqc_t2_all_brain_mean.Description: T2: Mean intensity within brain mask averaged across all scans

iqc_t2_ok_brain_mean.Description: T2: Mean intensity within brain mask averaged across all OK scans

iqc_t2_all_brain_std.Description: T2: Standard deviation of intensities within brain mask averaged across all scans

iqc_t2_ok_brain_std.Description: T2: Standard deviation of intensities within brain mask averaged across all OK scans

iqc_t2_fov_qc.Description: T2: Number with dorsal cutoff, ventral cutoff, or wrapping

iqc_t2_line_qc.Description: T2: Number with dark axial slices across the brain

iqc_t2_needrawqc.Description: T2: at least one series needs rawQC

iqc_t2_procfail.Description: T2: at least one series has a processing error before autoQC

iqc_t2_rename_err.Description: T2: Total number with rename error

iqc_t2_unpack_err.Description: T2: Total number with unpack errors

iqc_t2_waitautoqc.Description: T2:  at least one series is waiting for autoQC
